OL,3,CMP seeks business evidence after South
OL,4,CEast Water outage compensation row
OL,6,FThe MP for Tunbridge Wells is calling
OL,7,Fon local businesses to share their
OL,8,Fexperiences of the impact of water
OL,9,Foutages in an online consultation.
OL,11,FIt comes as South East Water announced
OL,12,Fthey would consider compensating
OL,13,Fbusinesses beyond the original
OL,14,Foffering of #600,000 if they received
OL,15,Fclear, evidenced claims.
OL,17,FThe Liberal Democrat, Mike Martin,
OL,18,Fcalled this initial offering of
OL,19,Froughly #400 per business "paltry" and
OL,20,F"insulting."
