OL,3,CMP seeks business evidence after South
OL,4,CEast Water outage compensation row
OL,6,FAt a parliamentary hearing in January,
OL,7,FMPs grilled water company boss David
OL,8,FHinton over this figure.
OL,10,FThey asked if South East Water would
OL,11,Fincrease business compensation if
OL,12,Fpresented with evidence that losses
OL,13,Fexceeded #600,000.
OL,15,FHinton indicated they would, stating
OL,16,Fthat the company will "absolutely look
OL,17,Fat the evidence before us."
