OL,3,CMP seeks business evidence after South
OL,4,CEast Water outage compensation row
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, (20 January) the
OL,7,Fgovernment announced water companies
OL,8,Fwill be required to carry out
OL,9,Finfrastructure "MOTs" to prevent major
OL,10,Ffailures under plans for a new
OL,11,Findustry watchdog.
OL,13,FAt the height of the incident, the
OL,14,Fcompany reported that 30,000 customers
OL,15,Facross the two counties were without
OL,16,Fwater, or experiencing low water
OL,17,Fpressure.
OL,19,FSchools were closed, businesses forced
OL,20,Fto shut and thousands of people had to
OL,21,Fget water at bottled water stations.
