OL,3,CMP seeks business evidence after South
OL,4,CEast Water outage compensation row
OL,6,FThe beleaguered water firm has faced
OL,7,Fheavy criticism from MPs and the
OL,8,Fpublic, as the outage came on the
OL,9,Fheels of a similar incident last
OL,10,Fmonth, where 24,000 people in
OL,11,FTunbridge Wells were left without
OL,12,Fdrinking water for two weeks.
OL,14,FAnyone who wants to be part of this
OL,15,Fcase, presented by Mr Martin, is asked
OL,16,Fto provide evidence of the losses
OL,17,Fsustained during the incidents, with
OL,18,Fall information kept confidential.
