OL,6,FIn a statement, South East Water's
OL,7,FCustomer Services Director, Tanya
OL,8,FSephton, said: "We are deeply sorry
OL,9,Ffor the impact this situation has had
OL,10,Fon residents and businesses in
OL,11,FTunbridge Wells.
OL,13,F"We abide by our Guaranteed Standards
OL,14,Fof Service (GSS) and we are fully
OL,15,Fcommitted to compensating our
OL,16,Fcustomers and businesses fairly for
OL,17,Fthis disruption.
